Package entity.Appointments

Class AppointmentOutcomeRecord

java.lang.Object
entity.Appointments.AppointmentOutcomeRecord
public class AppointmentOutcomeRecord extends Object
Represents the outcome of a medical appointment. Stores information such as the appointment ID, date, type, consultation notes, prescribed medications, and the associated doctor and patient.
